== Ezgraphix Online Demo!

Ezgraphix is a rails plugin to generate flash based graphics for rails applications using a free and customizable chart's set, Ezgraphix repository can be found in GitHub, and Ezgraphix documentation can be found in RubyForge. Developed by jpemberthy and relased under MIT license.

== Local Installation

git clone the project, rake db:migrate (database.yml included and using sqlite3), start server,thats it.